{"tid":1641102,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"紀念雙十，點少得十八星旗","createTime":"2019-10-09T08:45:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-10T07:56:31.000Z","uid":274161,"like":10,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"34b68116b11996d80040d6d55836dd4b262b2c4d","tid":1641102,"uid":274161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T08:45:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Lc77Tax.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLc77Tax.png&h=15e4d46e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n聽日就雙十了，大家準備點紀念呢？有無考慮過十八星旗呀？<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">歷史意義</span></strong>（from wiki）：<br />\n1911年10月10日，武昌起義打響辛亥革命第一槍。1911年9月，在同盟會推動下組成領導起義的總指揮部，定十八星旗為旗幟，也是起義后中華民國湖北軍政府宣告成立時所采用的旗幟。<br />\n<br />\n十八星旗設計理念：紅底與黑九角象徵「血」與「鐵」，即革命須抱鐵血主義；十八星代表十八行省。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">現實意義</span></strong>：<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">十八星代表香港十八區；<br />\n紅黑黃三色均與本次運動緊密相關：紅是熱血，黑是black bloc，黃是對雨傘運動的傳承。<br />\n<br />\n中間的星造型，暗示革命遍地開花，由近及遠，裏應外合。</span><br />\n<br />\n同盟會爲對抗清朝統治而成立，口號爲&ldquo;驅除韃虜,恢復中華&rdquo;。<br />\n今日的運動爲對抗中共對香港的侵略，同樣有口號&ldquo;<span style=\"color: red;\">驅除共黨，光復香港</span>&rdquo;。"},{"pid":"7e3ca8826882e5017e4232302baeee5f67924916","tid":1641102,"uid":269515,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T08:45:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">「Xinnie the Pooh」Challenge</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/q3PNSB7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fq3PNSB7.png&h=70fa4b5f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/a4UBLW8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fa4UBLW8.png&h=10505b4b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1. Draw your own &quot;Xinnie the Pooh&quot;<br />\n2. Write down what do you want to tell Chairman Xi<br />\n3. Post your work on ig, fb and twitter with tag #Xinniethepooh <br />\n4. Tag up to 3 more friends to draw together!"},{"pid":"b3304956a38c1539a1051d787ce3719b2baf7148","tid":1641102,"uid":2404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T08:46:18.000Z","msg":"十八區起義<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13791c03c774ef1f8308294e1f1bdf849918fe14","tid":1641102,"uid":325406,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T08:48:03.000Z","msg":"連個數字都岩"},{"pid":"8ac729cba19050320de929b7938680400ee46bbf","tid":1641102,"uid":288154,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T08:54:36.000Z","msg":"10月10 十十 雙十 公開祝賀盟幫<span style=\"color: red;\">中華民國</span>建國108年<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1640476\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1640476</a>"},{"pid":"e5530f26fc54cb6f420afe0bcf5bec72ab76588d","tid":1641102,"uid":28960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T13:27:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d079cec02e4acca53da9b30cd37a85acecec494c","tid":1641102,"uid":258706,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T13:38:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Qa6c5Vy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQa6c5Vy.jpg&h=3270050e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">毋忘烈士</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oEgXxAx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoEgXxAx.jpg&h=e2204c54&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">反清立民</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ksNLGtR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FksNLGtR.jpg&h=524f852b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"aeaf1246b46c805db62a75f52191f5cc6b99dfcf"